How to run APLUS application using the script files
Note that you need java 1.8.0 version in order to run this application.

For MAC/Linux users:

-> To run usual APLUS with existing modes:

1. cd AlgebraTuTalk
2. ./runAplus.sh

An example command to run APLUS in cog tutor mode:
./runAplus.sh -ct -noLogging

An example command to run APLUS with metatutor metacognitive hints mode:
./runAplus.sh -mtmc -noLogging

An example command to run APLUS with metatutor metacognitive hints mode and cti turned on:
./runAplus.sh -mtmc -cti -noLogging
